---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description:
		"Product release schedule for @cowsayco: a strategic roadmap from token launch through protocol automation, structured as three development epochs.",
	title: "Roadmap ‚Ä¢ @cowsayco",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<section>
		<h1 class="title mb-6">Product Release Schedule</h1>
		<p class="mb-4">
			Strategic development roadmap structured as three epochs: Genesis (launch & stability), The Flywheel (revenue streams), and The Protocol (automation & governance).
		</p>
		<p class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs text-muted">
			Strategic Horizon: 2025‚Äì2027 | Backed by on-chain vesting
		</p>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2 class="title mb-6 mt-16 text-2xl">Release Timeline</h2>
		<div class="mb-6 overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-accent bg-black p-4">
			<pre class="font-mono text-xs text-green-400">$ cat roadmap.txt</pre>
		</div>
		<div class="overflow-x-auto">
			<table class="w-full border-collapse font-mono text-xs">
				<thead>
					<tr class="border-b border-accent">
						<th class="p-2 text-left">Epoch</th>
						<th class="p-2 text-left">Timeline</th>
						<th class="p-2 text-left">Focus</th>
						<th class="p-2 text-left">Status</th>
					</tr>
				</thead>
				<tbody>
					<tr class="border-b border-accent/50">
						<td class="p-2">Epoch 1: Genesis</td>
						<td class="p-2">Weeks 0-4</td>
						<td class="p-2">Launch, vesting, stability</td>
						<td class="p-2"><span class="text-green-400">[DEPLOYS_IN_PROGRESS]</span></td>
					</tr>
					<tr class="border-b border-accent/50">
						<td class="p-2">Epoch 2: The Flywheel</td>
						<td class="p-2">Weeks 3-12</td>
						<td class="p-2">NFTs, merch, revenue streams</td>
						<td class="p-2"><span class="text-yellow-400">[BACKLOG]</span></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td class="p-2">Epoch 3: The Protocol</td>
						<td class="p-2">Months 3-36</td>
						<td class="p-2">Automation, airdrops, governance</td>
						<td class="p-2"><span class="text-muted">[BACKLOG]</span></td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2 class="title mb-6 mt-16 text-2xl">üõ†Ô∏è Epoch 1: Genesis</h2>
		<p class="mb-4 text-muted text-sm">
			Launch & Stability | Timeline: Weeks 0-4
		</p>
		<div class="mb-4 rounded border border-accent p-4">
			<h3 class="mb-3 font-bold font-mono text-sm">Milestones</h3>
			<ul class="mb-4 space-y-2">
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-green-400 font-mono text-xs">[COMPLETED]</span>
					<span>Website token pages deployed</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-green-400 font-mono text-xs">[COMPLETED]</span>
					<span>Documentation complete</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-yellow-400 font-mono text-xs">[DEPLOYS_IN_PROGRESS]</span>
					<span>Token creation on Pump.fun ‚Üí Raydium migration</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-yellow-400 font-mono text-xs">[DEPLOYS_IN_PROGRESS]</span>
