				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-muted font-mono text-xs">[BACKLOG]</span>
					<span>Contract address and wallet addresses published</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-muted font-mono text-xs">[BACKLOG]</span>
					<span>Launch announcement and community engagement</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-muted font-mono text-xs">[BACKLOG]</span>
					<span>Initial buyback execution from early revenue</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-muted font-mono text-xs">[BACKLOG]</span>
					<span>Community growth via Discord and X/Twitter</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-muted font-mono text-xs">[BACKLOG]</span>
					<span>Genesis NFT batch preview and teasers</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="mt-4 rounded border border-accent bg-accent/10 p-3">
				<p class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs font-semibold">The 3-Year Covenant</p>
				<p class="text-muted text-xs">
					A fixed commitment to ecosystem growth through 2027, backed by on-chain vesting. The creator allocation (200M tokens) is locked for 3 years, providing the strongest trust signal for long-term sustainability.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2 class="title mb-6 mt-16 text-2xl">üì¶ Epoch 2: The Flywheel</h2>
