		</p>
		<div class="mb-4 rounded border border-accent p-4">
			<h3 class="mb-3 font-bold font-mono text-sm">Milestones</h3>
			<ul class="mb-4 space-y-2">
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-muted font-mono text-xs">[BACKLOG]</span>
					<span>Genesis Collection launch: 5 unique developer quote NFTs</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-muted font-mono text-xs">[BACKLOG]</span>
					<span>NFT minting and auction mechanism deployment (Metaplex on Solana)</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
