					All NFT and merch proceeds are allocated 100% to $COWSAY token buybacks and burns, creating a deflationary mechanism that directly benefits token holders.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2 class="title mb-6 mt-16 text-2xl">üèõÔ∏è Epoch 3: The Protocol</h2>
