				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-muted font-mono text-xs">[BACKLOG]</span>
					<span>Sustainable revenue loop optimization</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="mt-4 rounded border border-accent bg-accent/10 p-3">
				<p class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs font-semibold">Strategic Horizon (2025‚Äì2027)</p>
				<p class="text-muted text-xs">
					The 3-year covenant extends through 2027, ensuring continuous ecosystem development, automated buybacks, and community governance. All revenue streams (merch, NFTs, partnerships) feed into the sustainable buyback mechanism, creating long-term value for token holders.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
